curc is a currency converter.

curc loads rates from ECB.

Usage:

    curc <amount> <from> <to>

Example:

    curc 150 USD EUR

Use "curc --help" for that information.
Use "curc --list" to print possible currencies.
Set "SCRIPTING" environment variable to print raw result.

